TITLE: Enabling and Starting Tangle Full Node Service
DESCRIPTION: Reloads the systemd daemon to recognize the new service file, enables the `full` service to start on boot, and starts the service immediately. Requires `sudo` privileges.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tangle-network/docs/blob/main/pages/operators/node-basics/systemd.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable full
sudo systemctl start full
```

