TITLE: Generating Tangle Node Key File
DESCRIPTION: Uses the compiled `tangle` binary to generate a new node key and save it to a specified file location. The `<BASE_PATH>` placeholder needs to be replaced with the actual base path for the node's data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tangle-network/docs/blob/main/pages/operators/node-basics/systemd.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
./target/release/tangle key generate-node-key \
--file <BASE_PATH>/node-key
```

