TITLE: Creating a Deployment Script for Tangle Network in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: A deployment script (deploy.js) for Hardhat to deploy smart contracts to Tangle Network. It includes logging the deployer's address and balance, deploying the contract, and logging the deployed contract's address.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tangle-network/docs/blob/main/pages/developers/technicals/deploy-using-hardhat.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
async function main() {
  const [deployer] = await ethers.getSigners();

  console.log(
    "Deploying contracts with the account:",
    deployer.address
  );

  console.log("Account balance:", (await deployer.getBalance()).toString());

  const Contract = await ethers.getContractFactory("<YourContract>");
  const contract = await Contract.deploy(<YourContractParameters>);

  console.log("Contract address:", contract.address);
}

main()
  .then(() => process.exit(0))
  .catch((error) => {
    console.error(error);
    process.exit(1);
  });
```

