SOURCE: https://github.com/tangle-network/docs/blob/main/pages/developers/blueprint-runner/building.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
#[derive(Clone, Debug, Deserialize, Serialize)]
pub struct SquareJobParams {
    pub number: u64,
}

#[async_trait]
impl Job for SquareJobParams {
    type Output = u64;
    async fn run(&self) -> Result<Self::Output> {
        Ok(self.number * self.number)
    }
}
```

