TITLE: Configuring Tangle Full Node Service
DESCRIPTION: This snippet creates a systemd service configuration file for running a Tangle Full Node. It includes settings for the node's base path, chain selection, RPC configuration, and other parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tangle-network/docs/blob/main/pages/operators/node-basics/systemd.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_28

