TITLE: Converting Substrate Address to EVM Address in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Script that converts a Substrate address to an EVM-compatible address by decoding the Substrate address and extracting the first 20 bytes, then converting to hexadecimal format.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tangle-network/docs/blob/main/pages/developers/technicals/evm-substrate-transfers.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { decodeAddress } from "https://esm.sh/@polkadot/util-crypto";
import { u8aToHex } from "https://esm.sh/@polkadot/util";

const input = Deno.args[0];
if (!input) {
  console.error("usage: deno run substrateToEvm.ts <SUBSTRATE_ADDRESS_HERE>");
  Deno.exit(1);
}
const accountId = decodeAddress(input);
const res = accountId.subarray(0, 20);
const output = u8aToHex(res);
console.log({ input, output });
// run using:
// $ deno run substrateToEvm.ts <SUBSTRATE_ADDRESS_HERE>
```

